# Welcome to jtrent238's FoodMod.
There is lots of food in this mod along with some other cool stuff.

* [ButterCandy](https://github.com/jtrent238/jtrent238FoodMod/wiki/ButterCandy)
* [Cakes](https://github.com/jtrent238/jtrent238FoodMod/wiki/Cakes)
* [CandyCane](https://github.com/jtrent238/jtrent238FoodMod/wiki/CandyCane)
* [ChickenLeg](https://github.com/jtrent238/jtrent238FoodMod/wiki/ChickenLeg)
* [Mutton](https://github.com/jtrent238/jtrent238FoodMod/wiki/Mutton)

#####Items
* [CandyCaneStick](https://github.com/jtrent238/jtrent238FoodMod/wiki/CandyCaneStick)

#####Blocks

#####Mobs
